      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·閔予小子之什·006.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">良耜.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>畟畟良耜，俶載南畝，播厥百穀，實函斯活。
或來瞻女，載筐及筥。其饟伊黍，其笠伊糾。
其鎛斯趙，以薅荼蓼，荼蓼朽止，黍稷茂止。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Very sharp are the excellent shares,
With which they set to work on the south-lying acres.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__song-minyuxiaozi-006__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
