      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·頌·閔予小子之什·006.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">良耜.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>穫之挃挃，積之栗栗，其崇如墉，其比如櫛，以開百室。
百室盈止，婦子寧止。殺時犉牡，有捄其角。
以似以續，續古之人。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>They sow their various kinds of grain,
Each seed containing in it a germ of life.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
